    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 guidance. Mesh convergence GCI < 2.1%, experimental comparison MAE 8.3%, RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all operating points. Total uncertainty budget (discretization + model form + boundary condition) is 11.8% at 90% coverage, within MRL 2 acceptance envelope. CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
